data.description: GREAT Corner House! Are you looking for privacy and a large space of land? This option is perfect for you! It will allow you to create a large terrace, swimming pool or simply expand the construction space of your next home. Located in the exclusive community of Cascara Lane in  Auburndale Florida. The open kitchen with a panoramic view of the living/dining room has a granite top of the highest quality. Enjoy the convenience of a breakfast bar and sliding doors leading to a screened porch at the back, allowing easy access to a spacious backyard already fenced, It's the perfect place to create a relaxing oasis to savor Florida sunsets. The appliances are made of stainless steel. This house comes with a smart technology, The master bedroom is spacious with a large dressing room. Convenience is key with an inside laundry room and mere minutes to Publix, restaurants, and lake access. Nearby are baseball fields, Auburndale downtown (8 mins), and the captivating Fantasy of Flight (8 mins). Explore Legoland, Dinosaur World and Disney Themes Park just 30 minutes away, and enjoy easy access to SR33 and I-4 for commuting to Tampa or Orlando.    Contact me for your presentation and make this house your next home!
